    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that balance sounds good in theory but i'm talking about real numbers here. i've heard a lot of people say that these hikes are basically just a way to punish small shops while big corporations can easily absorb the cost. is there actually data showing that these laws help a small town economy, or is that more of a political talking point?",
